PN,38101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FA trans adult who recently left school
OL,8,Fsays changing guidance in Jersey on
OL,9,Fhow to treat children who have gender
OL,10,Fdysphoria would increase shame and
OL,11,Fsecrecy amongst children.
OL,13,FGender dysphoria is when someone is
OL,14,Fquestioning their gender and has a
OL,15,Fpersistent sense of unease arising
OL,16,Ffrom a mismatch between a person's
OL,17,Fbiological sex and their gender
OL,18,Fidentity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FThey were speaking anonymously ahead
OL,8,Fof a Jersey States Assembly debate on
OL,9,Fthe guidance this week.
OL,11,FThey said: "I found that in school, I
OL,12,Fwas actually free to be myself, which
OL,13,Fis not something I had at home.
OL,14,FBecause I knew that whatever I told my
OL,15,Fteachers was confidential - it wasn't
OL,16,Fsomething that would make it home."
OL,18,FTheir parents found out about their
OL,19,Fgender dysphoria in another way and
OL,20,Fasked them to leave home because of it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FThey said: "It's a fear that I know a
OL,8,Flot of trans children have of their
OL,9,Fparents reacting in that way. Will I
OL,10,Ffind myself on the streets? Will I
OL,11,Fhave to apply for supported housing,
OL,12,Fwhich can be quite stressful for young
OL,13,Fpeople, and if they can't come to
OL,14,Fschool and feel supported as well,
OL,15,Fthat means that they don't have that
OL,16,Fenvironment in school either."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FThey went on to say: "We need to
OL,8,Fabandon this idea that calling a child
OL,9,Fby their preferred name is going to
OL,10,Flead them to having a surgery because
OL,11,Fit's not - legally, it cannot happen.
OL,12,FIt doesn't happen here. "
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FThey added: "I know as a trans person
OL,8,Fthat I am trans, and I knew this just
OL,9,Fas much five years ago as I do now.
OL,10,FThat doesn't mean that I should have
OL,11,Fbeen having surgery when I was a
OL,12,Fchild, but the simple acknowledgement
OL,13,Ffrom adults in my life that I was a
OL,14,Fperson, who had the right to be
OL,15,Fbelieved about this sort of thing, who
OL,16,Fhad the right to self-determination,
OL,17,Fwas so incredibly important."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FCurrently patients are only seen at
OL,8,FJersey's gender service clinic if they
OL,9,Fare 18 and over. The service provides
OL,10,Fassessment, diagnosis, and ongoing
OL,11,Fsupport for adults with gender
OL,12,Fidentity presentations. This may
OL,13,Finclude the prescribing of hormones
OL,14,Fand referral to the UK for surgery
OL,15,Fwhen this is indicated and meets the
OL,16,Fapproval criteria required.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FDeputy Sir Philip Bailhache has lodged
OL,8,Fa proposition to change the current
OL,9,Fguidance on how to treat children who
OL,10,Fare questioning their gender or who
OL,11,Fhave decided they are trans.
OL,13,FHe argues the current guidance is
OL,14,Fflawed and has been influenced too
OL,15,Fmuch by the equality and inclusion
OL,16,Fagenda to the detriment of
OL,17,Fsafeguarding children in general.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FHe said: "The existing guidance is
OL,8,Fmuddled and contradictory. It purports
OL,9,Fto express the view that schools have
OL,10,Fa responsibility to ensure that all
OL,11,Fchildren are safe and feel safe but at
OL,12,Fthe same time adopts an activist
OL,13,Fscript that children can be labelled
OL,14,Fas "trans" and therefore fall outside
OL,15,Fa normal safeguarding framework."
OL,17,FCurrent guidance:
OL,19,FNew proposals:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FThe proposed guidance was written by
OL,8,FUK campaigner Stephanie Davies Arai
OL,9,Fwho leads the group Transgender Trend,
OL,10,Fshe said: "We don't have the right to
OL,11,Fimpose that kind of language on other
OL,12,Fchildren. Children have a right to
OL,13,Ftheir own beliefs and speech. So
OL,14,Fasking a child to use the pronoun he
OL,15,Fabout a girl is really impacting on
OL,16,Fother children's rights."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FShe added: "Teenagers are developing
OL,8,Fautonomy and agency. We do impose
OL,9,Frules to protect teenagers, even
OL,10,Fthough they are developing autonomy
OL,11,Fand agency, that doesn't absolve us of
OL,12,Four responsibilities."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FShe went on to say: "There should be
OL,8,Fno affirmation or validation of
OL,9,Fidentities, but allowing to express
OL,10,Fthemselves within their friendship
OL,11,Fgroups, they can use each others
OL,12,Fpronouns, and explore their
OL,13,Fidentities. But the adults must be in
OL,14,Fa position where they hold the
OL,15,Fauthority. The impact will be on their
OL,16,Flives not yours."
OL,18,FJersey's Education Minister, Deputy
OL,19,FRob Ward disagrees and has responded
OL,20,Fsaying Jersey should not be influenced
OL,21,Fby what's happening in the UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FHe said: "I think it's a real shame
OL,8,Fthat we're having intervention from
OL,9,Foverseas groups and lobby groups and
OL,10,Fpressure groups. Looking at our own
OL,11,Flaws . We are not part of the UK
OL,12,Fidentity. We need to keep our
OL,13,Fidentity. Keep our care and keep
OL,14,Flooking after our children in the way
OL,15,Fwe want to."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FThe Children's Commissioner, Carmel
OL,8,FCorrigan said she identified concerns
OL,9,Fabout how certain rights under the
OL,10,FUnited Nations Convention on the
OL,11,FRights of the Child (UNCRC) have been
OL,12,Finterpreted in the proposed guidance.
OL,14,FShe said: "Under the UNCRC, to which
OL,15,FJersey has been committed for more
OL,16,Fthan a decade now, our island's
OL,17,Fchildren and young people have the
OL,18,Fright to have their views heard and
OL,19,Ftaken seriously in decisions that
OL,20,Faffect their lives. ."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FShe added: This obviously includes
OL,8,Fpolicies that shape their experience
OL,9,Fof school. To our knowledge, no
OL,10,Fconsultation with children has taken
OL,11,Fplace in relation to changing the
OL,12,Fguidance in question. "
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,F"We initially recommended that the
OL,8,Fproposition be withdrawn to allow for
OL,9,Fa more thorough Children's Rights
OL,10,FImpact Assessment to be completed and
OL,11,Freview of the proposed guidance to
OL,12,Ftake place. However, that advice was
OL,13,Fnot taken and the proposition will now
OL,14,Fbe debated by the States Assembly. We
OL,15,Ftherefore encourage States Members to
OL,16,Ftake account of the children's rights
OL,17,Fconsiderations we have raised when
OL,18,Fdebating the proposition."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773173478
OL,3,CTrans adult says changing school
OL,4,Cguidance on trans children will cause
OL,5,Charm
OL,7,FIn Guernsey the guidance on how
OL,8,Fchildren who are questioning their
OL,9,Fgender are treated in schools was
OL,10,Fupdated in 2024.
OL,12,FGuernsey's Committee for Education,
OL,13,FSport and Culture said: "Balancing the
OL,14,Frights of children and young people
OL,15,Fwho question their gender identity
OL,16,Fwith wider safeguarding considerations
OL,17,Fis complicated and nuanced. We
OL,18,Fconsider both national guidance and
OL,19,Fresearch, and our own ongoing dialogue
OL,20,Fwith schools."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G16/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
